title: Interference
description: The bonds of sibling loyalty are tested as Sue Storm-Richards (The Invisible Girl) and her brother Johnny Storm (The Human Torch) tell their versions of a story that may be a bit too fantastic to believe. Starring AnnaSophia Robb as Marcia Hardesty; Seth Barrish as Phil Sheldon; Method Man as Ben Urich; Louisa Krause as Susan Storm; Ehad Berisha as Johnny Storm.
author: originals@stitcher.com (MARVELS)
